In a recent commentary for the Financial Times, economist Dambisa Moyo urges business leaders to invest in Bitcoin. She argues that Bitcoin is a way to mitigate company risk; cryptocurrencies can provide solutions for doing business in emerging economies; and digital currencies augur an exciting new future of “currency platforms”. 



